<P>But the diuine Grace is oppo|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> against all these difficulties, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ich is mightier and stronger <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">n all thinges: vpon which al|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">attend all the documents and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">structions, which heereafter we shall deliuer.</P>
