<P>We read that <HI>Pharaoh</HI> dyd the same thinge tipically to the <NOTE PLACE="marg">Exod. 5.</NOTE> Children of Israell, who when they sayd that it was comman|ded vnto them of God, that they should goe into the wildernes, that they might sacryfice vnto
