<P>This is of so great moment, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">at of it alone dependeth the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">der of a spirituall life, as ma|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">festly is shewen by this Argu|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ent: In morall actions the end <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">he roote and the foundation that, which is to bee done: <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">refore if the endes be orde|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> after a due and right maner
