<P>Therefore to what study more excellent, or to what businesse more noble canst thou apply thy <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">inde? If thou be a friend vnto <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">cience, and desirest to bee taught <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ue Wisedome, bee secure and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ithout dread, God doth heere each his friendes and familiars <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ch deep misteries and secrets, as
