<P>By this it is manyfest, how gree|uously they erre, who relinquishe<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> their exercise, and vtterly cast it off, when as by and by they finde not diuine consolations, when they seeke for them, &amp; when they desire them.</P>
