<P><HI>Who are you,</HI> saith she, <HI>that haue tempted God? this manner of dea|ling</HI> <NOTE PLACE="marg">Iudith. 8.</NOTE> <HI>is not the way to procure mer|cy, but rather to prouoke anger, &amp; kindle furie. Doe you appoint a time for the mercy of the Lord? and set downe a day, when he should deliuer you?</HI></P>
