<P>This is to drinke of the pure cup <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">f obedience, which is not mi|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ed with any other liquor, which <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ight mitigate the bitternesse of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word">, but onely with the strength of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ertue.</P>
<P>This is that true touchstone, by which is tried who is golde, and who is lead: who is Gods true <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">iend, and who is false.</P>
<P>Tell me, whether shee be the <NOTE PLACE="marg">A Simily.</NOTE> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ore faithfull wife, and worthier
