<P>Although all these things ge|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">rally pertaine to all men, yet <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ore especially they belong vnto <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ung beginners, who as young <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ollers &amp; children must before <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> thinges beleeue; afterwardes <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">owing more expert and ripe,
