<P>This word <HI>Against</HI> I haue <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">t vsed well, I ought to haue <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">d <HI>Besides.</HI> Whatsoeuer doth <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">er it selfe vnto consideration, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ich doth not by some meane <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">other pertaine vnto saluation, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">se and renounce it.</P>
<P>This also ought to moue them <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">t be studious, that so they giue <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">selues to promote the profit of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ir neighbor, that they doe not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">t nor hinder their own saluati|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> &amp; <HI>y^e</HI> they diligently take heed,
