<P>These things being thus, wee may easily gather, that from what fountaine soeuer consolations do flow, that a man hath no reason <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">o be prowde of the~, or too much <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">o glory in them.</P>
