<P>Yet let it be, that all the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> consolations are of God: yet <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> must consider that these fau<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> and graces are not giuen vnto <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> that we should be puffed vp, a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> despise our neighbour, but <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">, that wee should more se<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">|uently loue God, and that w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> should be humbled before othe<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"></P>
